oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Porter Wagoner Show at the City Auditorium (16154)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wagoner, Porter; Rhodes, Speck; Magaha, Mack; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the Porter Wagoner Show featuring Barbara Lea, Speck Rhodes, and the Wagonmasters at the City Auditorium in Rome, Georgia on March 1. Poster features metal photoplates of Porter Wagoner, Barbara Lea, and Speck Rhodes. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39856.
